text: Dilip Mane () is a Shiv Sena politician from Solapur district. He was a member of Maharashtra Legislative Assembly representing Solapur South constituency from 2009 to 2014. ==Positions held== * 2009: Elected as Member of Maharashtra Legislative Assembly ==References== ==External links== * The Shivsena Category:Members of the Maharashtra Legislative Assembly Category:Living people Category:People from Solapur district Category:Marathi politicians Category:Shiv Sena politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
